title: has_body_part()
brief: Does this message have a MIME part of the given type?
seealso: on_get_body, get_body_part, count_body_parts, get_body_parts
version: 0.20
----

<p>This function return TRUE if the current message has a MIME-part of the given content-type.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
if ( has_body_part( "image/jpg" ) ) then
   <a href="/lua/msg.html">msg</a>( "This message contains an image" )
end
</pre>